          you entered is correct or in correct form.<br />- Check spelling
          errors.<br /><span style="color: gray">That's all we know</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <div class="img-container">
          <img src="../images/robot.png" alt="robot" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
